(28, 5, 1, 'North Korea declares itself a nuclear weapons state', 'North Korea has passed a law declaring itself to be a nuclear weapons state, according to state news agency KCNA.', '&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;The country\\\'s leader Kim Jong-un called the decision \\&quot;irreversible\\&quot; and ruled out the possibility of any talks on denuclearisation, it said.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;The law also enshrines the country\\\'s right to use a pre-emptive nuclear strike to protect itself.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;Despite crippling sanctions, Pyongyang has conducted six nuclear tests between 2006 and 2017.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;It has continued to advance its military capability - in breach of United Nations Security Council resolutions - to threaten its neighbours and potentially even bring the US mainland within striking range.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;Mr Kim carried out long-range launches and nuclear tests in 2019 following two headline-grabbing but inconclusive summits with then US president Donald Trump.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;unordered-list-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1o5f7ft-BulletListContainer e5tfeyi0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;ul role=\\&quot;list\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=\\&quot;https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-41174689\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1no5rhv0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration-thickness: 1px; text-decoration-color: rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\&quot;&gt;What we know about N Korea\\\'s missile and nuclear programme&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=\\&quot;https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-62587445\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1no5rhv0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration-thickness: 1px; text-decoration-color: rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\&quot;&gt;Wargaming a North Korean attack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;But talks between the countries have since stalled. Although the Biden administration has indicated it\\\'s willing to talk to Pyongyang, it hasn\\\'t said whether President Joe Biden would meet Mr Kim.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;The White House also said its attempts to contact Pyongyang and overtures of help over its Covid outbreak had gone unanswered so far.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;The US reviewed its North Korea policy last year and reiterated that \\&quot;complete denuclearisation\\&quot; of the Korean peninsula was the goal. Mr Biden said he would pursue it with a mix of diplomacy and \\&quot;stern deterrence\\&quot;. Mr Kim responded by saying his country must prepare for both \\&quot;dialogue and confrontation\\&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;Meanwhile, tensions on the Korean peninsula have spiked this year with Pyongyang firing a record number of ballistic missiles.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;South Korea and the US have responded with a volley of missiles and the largest joint military exercises on the peninsula in years.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'http://localhost/ci4_blog/public/uploads/_126648423_7f03e15888fd53f903665fbc2824e9374420c22d.jpg', 'northkorea, nuclear weapons state', 1, '2022-09-10 11:19:38', '2022-09-10 11:19:38'),
(29, 5, 1, 'Ukraine has retaken 1,000 square kilometres in a week - Zelensky', 'Ukraine says it has retaken more than 1,000 sq km (385 sq miles) of territory in its south and east from Russia in the past week.', '&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;President Volodymyr Zelensky said that more than 30 settlements had been \\&quot;liberated\\&quot; in the Kharkiv region.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;Russia\\\'s top occupation official in Kharkiv region conceded Ukrainian forces had won a \\&quot;significant victory\\&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;Vitaly Ganchev told Russian TV that the Ukrainians had broken through the Russian defence line.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;He said civilians were being evacuated from Kupiansk, one of the most important urban centres in the Russian-held part of Kharkiv, and two other towns.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;According to analysis by the Institute for the Study of War think tank, Kyiv\\\'s troops are now just 15km (9 miles) from Kupiansk, home to an essential railway junction that Moscow has been using to supply its troops on the battlefield.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;Russia is believed to be sending reinforcements to the region by road and by air, using giant Mi-26 transport helicopters, each capable of carrying 80 soldiers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;In a separate Facebook post Ukraine\\\'s army said that in three days troops had advanced 50km (30 miles). If verified, that would mark the fastest movement of the front line since the rapid retreat of Russian forces from positions around the capital, Kyiv, in March.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;The offensive south-east of Kharkiv would also bring Ukraine\\\'s troops closer to the eastern region of Donetsk,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=\\&quot;https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-60938544\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-k17ofw-InlineLink e1no5rhv0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: none; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); text-decoration-thickness: 1px; text-decoration-color: rgb(138, 140, 142); text-decoration-skip-ink: none; text-underline-offset: 0.25em;\\&quot;&gt;over which Russia has maintained substantial military control&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;since the war began six months ago.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;Mr Ganchev also denied that Ukrainian forces had recaptured the town of Balakliya despite a video appearing to show Ukrainian soldiers there.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-component=\\&quot;text-block\\&quot; class=\\&quot;ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph eq5iqo00\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\\&quot;&gt;The BBC has not been able to confirm who has control of the city, but verified social media posts show Ukrainian flags flying from administrative buildings in the city\\\'s centre on Thursday.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'http://localhost/ci4_blog/public/uploads/_126652957_gettyimages-1243044518.jpg.webp', 'war, Ukraine vs Russia', 1, '2022-09-10 11:25:49', '2022-09-10 11:25:49'),
(30, 2, 1, 'Cheating Allegations Shake the Chess World After Champion Suffers Stunning Defeat', 'World champion Magnus Carlsen withdrew from the Sinquefield Cup after being beaten by a 19-year-old he implied may have cheated.', '&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;For those who think the high-stakes world of professional chess is about as exciting as watching paint dry, think again.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;Allegations of cheating have shaken up the upper echelons of the intellectual game, including one player being frisked for a device that might have helped him analyze moves.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;The controversy surrounds the withdrawal of World Champion Magus Carlsen from the $350,000 Sinquefield Cup in St. Louis on Monday after he was beaten by a 19-year-old grandmaster who was once kicked off an online gaming site for using a computer to analyze his moves.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;Hans Niemann, the upstart, beat the Norwegian champ in the third round, prompting Carlsen to leave the tournament, after which he posted a cryptic message on his social media in the form of a video of soccer manager José Morinho, who referred to a cheating scandal among referees with: “If I speak I am in big trouble.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;color: rgb(2, 20, 31); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;Storylines\\&quot; id=\\&quot;storylines-target-middle\\&quot; style=\\&quot;padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;The cheating suggestion quickly went viral, causing Niemann to deny the allegations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;“It must be embarrassing for the world champion to lose to me,” Niemann, who was seeded last in the tournament said. “I feel bad for him.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;Niemann was once removed from an online competition after it was discovered he was using a computer to analyze moves, but he insisted he has never cheated in a live, in-person competition. “I’m telling the world because I do not want any misrepresentation, and I do not want rumors,” he said this week. “I have never cheated in an over-the-board game.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;Nevertheless, he was “thoroughly frisked” during the next round of play for a computing device that could have helped him analyze his moves in the competition, which carries a $350,000 purse. No device was found, but the competition was delayed by 15 minutes, causing at least some embarrassment to the newcomer, according to&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;The&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Guardian&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;The scandal reminded many of the 2006 “Toiletgate” debacle in which Veselin Topalov accused opponent Vlad Kramnik of having planted a device in the toilet to help analyze moves.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;Several players in this week’s St. Louis tournament&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=\\&quot;LinkWrapper LinkWrapper--external\\&quot; href=\\&quot;https://www.wsj.com/articles/magnus-carlsen-hans-niemann-chess-cheating-scandal-11662644458?cx_testId=3&amp;amp;cx_testVariant=cx_5&amp;amp;cx_artPos=1&amp;amp;mod=WTRN#cxrecs_s\\&quot; style=\\&quot;background-color: transparent; color: inherit; transition: color 0.15s ease 0s;\\&quot;&gt;told the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Wall Street Journal&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;that they were unable to concentrate because of the scandal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;Top contender Ian Nepomniachtchi, said that the only way to ensure secret buzzers or devices were not being used could come down to competing “naked in a locked room” to keep the game clean.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;line-height: 31px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 19px; padding: 0px calc(32px + ((100% - 176px) / 12) * 2); color: rgb(40, 55, 65); font-family: Georgia, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;\\&quot;&gt;“I don’t see this happening,” the Russian—who lost to Carlsen for the World Chess Championship—told the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Journal&lt;/em&gt;, but said he was shocked that the younger Niemann beat Carlsen, calling it “more than impressive.”&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://localhost/ci4_blog/public/uploads/GettyImages-1230825845_wakoix.jpg', 'chess,', 1, '2022-09-10 17:44:05', '2022-09-10 17:44:05');

